             UNPACK    DRGFDTE,CCENT,CYEAR,CMON,CDAY
          ELSE
             GOTO   SDAT0500
          ENDIF
.
SDAT0700  MOVE      TEN7,CVERT                   * default to start of year date
          MOVE      TEN3,CCOL
.
          CALL      KEYDATE
